{"tid":186240,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"接力改歌詞：念念不忘","createTime":"2017-04-04T05:22:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-04T11:42:40.000Z","uid":24266,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"452debc45d211fc167a59cfb1ce3039855226a40","tid":186240,"uid":24266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T05:22:00.000Z","msg":"接力改歌詞<br />\n原詞：念念不忘<br />\n舊情未會化<br />\n十六年未會怕<br />\n縱使你困在紅葉下<br />\n化做了花<br />\n十里殷殷秋葉再落下<br />\n野菊開過了<br />\n又新開花<br />\n你不變    永是笑靨如花<br />\n<br />\n藏着往事的秋花<br />\n當初那美麗從不淡化<br />\n未像你寫的童話<br />\n舊日理想飛散如沙<br />\n<br />\n你以後不再痛心興奮快樂沒有牽掛<br />\n卻較人心裏額上憂鬱苦痛沒法抑壓<br />\n皓雪寒風再折返今天縱使秋意闌珊<br />\n看風霜片片夜夜來為難<br />\n等一天血染綠葉再秋發<br />\n<br />\n落紅是你嗎   特地來問訊嗎<br />\n晚秋摯愛是紅葉吧<br />\n領悟到嗎<br />\n（輪到你改了）"},{"pid":"50ddbb2573017b3718d6e93f41355baa43dd550f","tid":186240,"uid":40429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T05:41:50.000Z","msg":"幾好，環繞住「秋」又冇離題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n提意你可以於詞末加上「十七年蟬」作終於離開、放下嘅意象，呼應開首「十六年」之餘又可以食住自然之物去將意思昇華<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83b86159f69f7d0e11a1a53ecf6c9b179b12c44c","tid":186240,"uid":11799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T05:47:00.000Z","msg":"尚有花辦飄散滿地下<br />\n我怎麼會怕 未可賞花<br />\n美可以 永續到未來嗎"},{"pid":"7dd70aebc90e1f781665075b7e06937dec0edbb8","tid":186240,"uid":24266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T06:40:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幾好，環繞住「秋」又冇離題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n提意你可以於詞末加上「十七年蟬」作終於離開、放下嘅意象，呼應開首「十六年」之餘又可以食住自然之物去將意思昇華<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"http://forum5.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?type=MU&amp;message=6696521\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fforum5.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Ftype%3DMU%26message%3D6696521&d=iVnpHeK512wFMD%2FK5G8l3cVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=dac500a8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://forum5.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?type=MU&amp;message=6696521</a><br />\n本來見到你地係度傾想搭訕，但係可惜冇高登帳"},{"pid":"f07bf90f245b2ab02970890e2c8dfedba1d2a53e","tid":186240,"uid":90596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T07:28:33.000Z","msg":"留名學野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f75d6ffeb97cf1a1d9fe65337629f2ee15368f81","tid":186240,"uid":24266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T11:42:40.000Z","msg":"推"}]}